How to manage products when you grow:
Stage 1 — Right now (1-200 products)

You have ONE file: data/products.json
Everything works fine, no changes needed
Stage 2 — When you reach 200-500 products

The "Load More" button is already working
Customers see 20 at a time, page stays fast
You still use ONE products.json file
Stage 3 — When you reach 500+ products

Open admin.html
Click "Export by Category" instead of "Export products.json"
It downloads separate files:
products-dresses.json (only dresses)
products-tops.json (only tops)
products-bottoms.json (only bottoms)
etc.
Put these files in data/ folder
Delete the big products.json
Site automatically loads only what's needed → stays fast
